Package org.universAAL.ui.dm.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAdapter
    Interface for all Dialog Manager adaptations.
    IDialogBuilder
    Implementations Of this Interface Build dialogs and show them to the user.
    IMainMenuProvider
    Provides the main menu for a certain user.
    ISubmitGroupListener
    Listen to a set of SubmissionIDs and handle the UIResponse corresponding to any of them.
    ISystemMenuProvider
    Used to generate System group.
    IUIPreferencesBuffer
    An entry point to the Preffences buffer.
    IUIPreferencesChangeListener
    Implementations of this interface can be added as listeners for changes in a UIPreferencesSubProfile.
    IUIRequestPool
    Manage UIRequests.
    IUIRequestStore
    Implementations of this interface will save and restore IUIRequestPools, each implementing a different permanence mechanism.
